2. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the social-worker##1
3. the person driving the van is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |
| Hobby         | dancing      | writing       |
| Job           | entrepreneur | social-worker |
| Movie-Genre   | western      | horror        |
| Cigar   | vegafina         | oliveros        |
| Birthday   | may    | september       |
| Pet           | mouse        | goat          |
| Transport     | van          | snowmobile    |

