.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-3::.
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, fish
There 2 different types of food: lettuce, pomegranate
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, rock-climbing
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, teacher
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, egyptian
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, ice-hockey
City: liverpool, paris
1. the person traveling to paris is on the left or right of the dancer##3
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
3. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the argentine##3
4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
5. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |
| Pet      | goldfish | fish  |
| Food          | pomegranate   | lettuce   |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | puzzles   |
| Job           | dancer        | teacher   |
| Nationality   | egyptian      | argentine |
| Sport         | ice-hockey    | climbing  |
| City     | liverpool       | paris      |

