The people prefer 2 different music-genres: jazz, salsa
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: rose, poppy
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, water-polo
The people have 2 different jobs:  nurse, musician
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1
2. the nurse is on the right of the musician##1
3. the person who growsrose is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
4. the musician is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk   | juice      |
| Food          | strawberry    | apricot    |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | card-games |
| Music-Genre   | salsa         | jazz       |
| Flower           | poppy      | rose   |
| Sport         | cycling       | water-polo |
| Job     | musician         | nurse       |

